            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">✅ Success Story</h3>
            <p>
                "With SyncTime, I found that Ticketmaster's server was 0.8 seconds slower than my computer.
                So I refreshed at 13:59:59.2, and finally got the sold-out ticket!" - Anonymous User
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2>Precautions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>SyncTime is a <strong>reference tool</strong>. It does not guarantee 100% accuracy.</li>
            <li>Errors may occur depending on network conditions.</li>
            <li>High server load can increase server response times.</li>
            <li>Illegal macros or bots are strictly prohibited.</li>
        </ul>
        <% } %>